<br>
"Their User agreement is a contract and, as with any contract, there are expectations that are held by all parties concerned. To say that Verant's can ban anyone for any reason, diregards two key issues. The first being the laws dealing with discrimination. Second are the expectations that can be reasonbly assumed from the wording and intent of the contract itself.<br>
